page.title: 14WILD FLOWERS - WIRKSWORTH
page.content: THE AREA IS FAMOUS FOR WILD FLOWERS THAT GROW ON LIMESTONE AND THE SPOIL HEAPS FROM LONG DISUSED LEAD MINES. ON A WALK THROUGH THE COUNTRY-SIDE AROUND THE SOUTHERN EDGES OF WIRKSWORTH WE FOUND THE FOLLOWING. WE HAVE NOT INCLUDED THE VERY FAMILIAR.
